<% content_for :title do %>
  Global Cybersecurity at Manulife
<% end %>
<div style="height: 100px;"></div>
<div class="mx-5 text-light">
  <div class="row justify-content-center align-items-center mx-0 mb-5">
    <div class="col-auto text-center">
      <%= image_tag("manulife_logo.jpg", alt: "Manulife", height: 80) %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-auto ps-4">
      <p class="fw-bold font-monospace my-0" style="font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3rem);">Cyber Security Analyst</p>
      <p class="text-opacity-75 font-monospace my-0" style="font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);">May 2022 &ndash; August 2022 &middot; Toronto, ON</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="height: 40px;"></div>
  <div class="row mx-0 justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-lg-9 col-xxl-8">
      <p class="text-start text-opacity-75 mb-4" style="font-size: 1.15rem;">
        As a Cyber Security Analyst intern at Manulife's Global Cybersecurity Services (GCS) team, I focused
        on automating and modernizing internal security processes. I built out automated onboarding workflows
        using Microsoft Power Apps and Power Automate, reducing manual onboarding steps by 70% and ensuring
        new users were consistently provisioned in line with corporate cybersecurity standards.
      </p>
      <p class="text-start text-opacity-75 mb-4" style="font-size: 1.15rem;">
        I developed a centralized Power Apps portal backed by SharePoint for 50+ team leads and managers,
        streamlining employee data management that had previously been scattered across disconnected systems.
        The portal gave leadership a single source of truth for team information and significantly reduced
        the overhead of maintaining records across multiple lists.
      </p>
      <p class="text-start text-opacity-75 mb-4" style="font-size: 1.15rem;">
        I also designed and built an ELT data pipeline using Power Automate and Azure Data Factory, feeding
        live-updated Power BI dashboards for upper management analytics. Additionally, I conducted security
        audits on onboarding processes to identify gaps and ensure compliance with Manulife's corporate
        cybersecurity standards.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div style="height: 150px;"></div>